commit.message:
Makefile.in (builtins.o): Depend on tree-mudflap.h.

[gcc/ChangeLog]
2004-09-08  Andreas Tobler  <toa@pop.agri.ch>

        * Makefile.in (builtins.o): Depend on tree-mudflap.h.
        * builtins.c: Include tree-mudflap.h.

From-SVN: r87175
